n.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打 我留意左你好耐 你眞係好幽默 我自問都算係個ok幽默既人 但係你幽默感眞係高我十幾廿倍 唔係 應該係100倍先啱 估唔到我竟然喺呢個post見識到你嘅威力 我眞係笑到爆左肚 而家一路打字一路執返啲腸啊內臟啊腎啊 塞返落個肚到 你有無諗過未來幾個月去紅館開棟篤笑?"},{"pid":"e0521dc2563032c51ba77cdf79b02063dbb2304b","tid":408134,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:05:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新移民先嘔嘔聲<br />\n香港已死</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />on9<br />\n傳統廣東話先多變調"},{"pid":"dff69b814a69b14aa56795841f5809b856b5fddc","tid":408134,"uid":18001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:06:18.000Z","msg":"林sir----&gt;撚sir"},{"pid":"d6bf3d223a4b5a8858eb98559323a9ad23fa946d","tid":408134,"uid":18001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:06:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>林sir----&gt;撚sir</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係諗sir"},{"pid":"cd1ec7aaeccbbe3f01e4fe5f4425522ac5884710","tid":408134,"uid":104748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:10:53.000Z","msg":"免治嘔飯"},{"pid":"3979c45a32a09880aa51381016da02e8f7d9d192","tid":408134,"uid":28876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:18:34.000Z","msg":"奇畫定奇華"},{"pid":"19404b590fdd824b386746b176879583f8cdd882","tid":408134,"uid":39426,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"因為牛要壓低音，係餐廳呢d. 環境咁嘈雜既地方好易會聽錯同聽漏<br />\n<br />\n但讀嘔就係響音，容易大聲叫出黎，等伙記廚房都易聽到<br />\n<br />\n係咪我認真左"},{"pid":"07fd2fbf5b457a6fb888466d36a32601aca6f7b5","tid":408134,"uid":68065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:37:43.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？咁叫先夠地道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c304b30bb943bb6dddb362fe5570668a92de3c71","tid":408134,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r